################################################################################
# CODEOWNERS — Invariant ownership boundaries
#
# This file defines who must review changes to each part of the codebase.
# Adding or moving a crate MUST be accompanied by a matching CODEOWNERS entry.
# The ownership model follows the architectural layers defined in docs/ARCHITECTURE.md.
#
# Run `python3 scripts/codeowners-check.py` to validate coverage.
#
# Syntax:
#   *      = default fallback (all unmatched paths)
#   /path/ = directory-level ownership
#   *.ext  = file-extension-level ownership
################################################################################

# ── Default fallback ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Everything not matched below requires the repository maintainer.
*                                                                              @carabistouflette

